{"tid":1609324,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"咪撚屌612住！","createTime":"2019-10-01T14:17:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T15:48:25.000Z","uid":159997,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"61895c61fca6e17abcf2dd21aa493412bcb885ab","tid":1609324,"uid":159997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:17:33.000Z","msg":"緊係睇埋呢獲先決定大唔大大力屌鳩佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n強烈要求612批錢俾中槍義士全家逃亡<br />\n如果中槍義士無死，港共肯定出刀手甚至槍搞佢同佢屋企人。<br />\n希望當佢情況有好轉就即刻秘密送去外國，<br />\n將來送上聯合國做核彈。<br />\n612要安排到佢地平安去到之餘仲要佢地食得好住得好！<br />\n咁都唔肯612就係人血饅頭！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a170e84ec378eb745183a348f4ea9d9c7f448c71","tid":1609324,"uid":159997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:17:40.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"bf3ce30183bee699f5c4dc719872791025e1eb44","tid":1609324,"uid":159997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:18:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"32c02f64df775efe14cd5f6b45a7cf9064559d2f","tid":1609324,"uid":38204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:20:15.000Z","msg":"依家走 死咗都通知唔到屋企人喎"},{"pid":"ab1eb2af4433e68ff15dc6271742e166d2c1f7ad","tid":1609324,"uid":207084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:20:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3a64d66f6ed751060c38c52646b8090c1680f23a","tid":1609324,"uid":159997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32c02f64df775efe14cd5f6b45a7cf9064559d2f","tid":1609324,"uid":38204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:20:15.000Z","msg":"依家走 死咗都通知唔到屋企人喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:31:20.000Z","msg":"佢全家一齊走"},{"pid":"60651fc5cc03aaea1d1b3b70eda2b100df424136","tid":1609324,"uid":159997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab1eb2af4433e68ff15dc6271742e166d2c1f7ad","tid":1609324,"uid":207084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10